Regency Cruises Inc said its boardelected William Schanz as its chairman and chief executiveofficer. He replaces Anastasios Kyriakides, who resigned inDecember.    Schantz has served as president, treasurer, and a directorsince its inception in 1984.    The company also elected three directors. They are PaulHermann, John Clive Bayley and Costas Galetakis. The companysaid they replace Paul Wells and Douglas MacGarvey, who alsoresigned in December. One new director's post has been added,Regency said. Reuter&#3;